{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Somber Echoes is a dark-fantasy metroidvania rooted in ancient Greek mythologies.\u00a0You shall set out to stop your twin sister from destroying the universe and venture into the challenges and mysteries ahead, to find the answers to the questions hidden under the ashes of a impending destruction of the worlds. The decisions you make when you play determine your fate and ending of the game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cataclysmic event turned the once beautiful and proud Greco-Roman space vessel Atromitos into breeding grounds for infested horrors from an unknown dimension. In the aftermath, a mysterious force choses to interfere with destiny and awaken Adrestia from rubble and ashes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Adrestia, your mission is to stop your twin sister Harmonia from unraveling the universe, but many questions remain unanswered. In the search for answers you explore the vast space vessel while gaining powers, knowledge and skills that might shape your ultimate destiny.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a Metroidvania where combat is about mastering acrobatic freedom. Explore an environment that embraces diverse gameplay styles to suit every player. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stunning environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautifully crafted distinct districts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/enviroments.gif?t=1737467446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple \u00abbiomes\u00bb:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/Multiple_biomes.png?t=1737467446\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master perfect parry to gain advantage in combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/parryandimpale.gif?t=1737467446\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/perfectparry.gif?t=1737467446\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Progressive traversal  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/Wallrun_traversal.gif?t=1737467446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/hover.gif?t=1737467446\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story inspired by Greek tragedies and Greek Mythology </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique Greco-Roman science fiction setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Visceral combat and acrobatic player freedom </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple distinctive districts (biomes) with their own visual identity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple endings: how you play determines how you complete the game</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"No stone left unturned","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1299290/9c61cd889dd0627e2a6f6dc9de8fe883240c9480.jpg"},{"name":"Back from the Dead","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1299290/9c61cd889dd0627e2a6f6dc9de8fe883240c9480.jpg"},{"name":"Circe","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1299290/9c61cd889dd0627e2a6f6dc9de8fe883240c9480.jpg"},{"name":"Fully operational","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1299290/9c61cd889dd0627e2a6f6dc9de8fe883240c9480.jpg"},{"name":"In perfect health","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1299290/9c61cd889dd0627e2a6f6dc9de8fe883240c9480.jpg"},{"name":